  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study hypothesis is that caregivers experience allows them to develop a lot of knowledge
      and know-how about behavioural problems in Huntington Disease and its consequences. The
      purpose of this study is to collect, describe and analyse caregivers experience in order to
      find and enhance their knowledge related to the adaptation to behavioural problems of
      Huntington Disease patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
